107
00:05:45.466 --> 00:05:47.050
I... I have to call them.

108
00:05:47.134 --> 00:05:48.844
We just have one more
question. I promise.

109
00:05:48.927 --> 00:05:51.555
Can you tell us why your husband was

110
00:05:51.680 --> 00:05:53.557
